{"word":"ἀναμένω","slug":"ἀναμένω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναμένω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to wait for, await</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> et <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>ἀν. τινὰ ποιεῖν</el> <i>to await</i> one's doing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>ἀν. τι γίνεσθαι</el> a thing happening, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—absol <i>to wait, stay</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to await, endure</i>, <el>τί</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to put off, delay</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}